{
  "name": "RPlog_Audience_with_Mighty_Juuka",
  "title": "Audience with Mighty Juuka",
  "summary": "New Republic Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard travels to the Tatooine palace of the Hutt crime lord Juuka during his lavish festivities, escorted by her protocol droid TC-81 and a small armed guard. After negotiating the palace's two-guest limit with the Devaronian majordomo Emmit, she presents Juuka with a sled of lavish tribute -- coveted tomuon cloth, holo-tapestries of Hutt glory, and a crystalline Shownar hookah -- gradually winning the greedy slug's favor. With the formalities satisfied, Ambrosia reveals her true purpose: the systematic abduction of thousands of Wookiees from Kashyyyk by the Trandoshan Bloodclaw clan, transported through a third party to an unknown destination. She appeals to Juuka's vast informant network for intelligence and a reliable contact. Juuka agrees to provide information and broker an introduction to a like-minded mercenary in exchange for unmolested free passage of his ships through Republic space, and the two strike a wary trade accord before Ambrosia takes her leave.",
